---
title: Creamy Parma Ham & Parmigiano Filled Pasta with Pesto and Courgette
description: Looking for a quick and tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Creamy Parma Ham & Parmigiano Filled Pasta in just 20-25 minutes for a delicious and speedy meal.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/HF_Y24_R05_W06_UK_R17747-3_Main_low-f95a50b1.jpg
